# Self Description - Volunteer

## Background
Seeks ethical work opportunities that balance immediate needs with long-term family reunification.

Priorities include Right Livelihood work that sustains both practice and family responsibilities through platforms like [HelpX](https://www.helpx.net) or temple connections.

## Immediate Goal
The path forward combines short-term stabilization (meeting basic needs through Sangha support or skill-bartering) with strategic steps toward reunification (visa-compliant work).

